Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: cutlass
Version: 0.0.0
Summary: Modular library for writing WSGI apps
Home-page: https://github.com/sashahart/cutlass
Author: Sasha Hart
Author-email: s@sashahart.net
License: LICENSE
Description: Cutlass is a radically modular WSGI library. It focuses on "a la carte"
        components which reduce boilerplate for basic web concerns like parsing
        and routing requests, generating responses, and coping with errors.
        
        This isn't mature yet. Documentation and examples need a lot of work and the
        API is still in flux.
        
